CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

April 22, 2014

[Cite as 04/22/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-1701.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-0579. In re D.M.

Hamilton App. No. C-120794, 2013-Ohio-668. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County.

Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to file the exhibits to the motion for stay under seal, it is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.
